@startuml
title Printer State Diagram

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> Receiving_Data : Print Command Sent
Receiving_Data --> Processing : Data Received
Processing --> Printing : Printer Ready

Printing --> Completed : Job Finished
Completed --> Idle : Return to Standby

' Pause / Resume
Printing --> Paused : Pause Command
Paused --> Printing : Resume Command

' Error Handling (can occur from almost any state)
Idle --> Error : Hardware Failure
Receiving_Data --> Error : Connection Lost
Processing --> Error : Data Corrupted
Printing --> Error : Paper Jam / Out of Ink

Error --> Idle : Reset / Issue Resolved

@enduml
